OOC: Jus so you know, Squawktalk had fired on you too.

BIC: Beastbox got hit in the head by the leg, and his hands let go, he
almost fell, but his feet held him firmly in place, his leg motors,
strained as he righted himself and shot once more into the same area he hit
before, now hoping it was weak, he tried to plunge one of his arms into the
metal he had been shooting.
